events.name: Lets talk about Project Management!
events.description: Lets get together over a drink and share some tips and experience in dealing with challenging projects. This meet up will be conducted in a relaxed atmosphere so chillax! Free snacks will be provided. Bumped into troubles in your projects? Feel free to toss in questions and let the group give some feedback to you. If you have one topic or two that you would like to talk about, dont hesitate to bring them up as well. The meet up will follow the lean coffee structure. Everybody can suggest a topic or two, and then vote on the topic that interest them. One person can vote twice and may use all their votes on one topic. Topics get the most votes will get the spot light and will be selected for the night.
events.location: Kazbar , 25 Church Street #01-03 Capital Square 3 Singapore 049482
